					五、參考書籍




					1.          
					

					(美)梅爾清著、朱修春譯，《清初揚州文化》，上海：復旦大學，2004。



					2.          
					

					Brook, Timothy The Confusions of Pleasure: Commerce 
					and Culture in Ming China. Berkeley and Los Angeles: 
					University of California Press. 1998.



